<div id="home" class="background">
  <div class="container parallax-bg">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-12">
        <div class="swiper-container">
            <div class="swiper-wrapper">
                <div class="swiper-slide"><iframe class="video" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/146656196?autoplay=0&amp;loop=0&amp;color=8D8292&amp;title=0&amp;byline=0&amp;portrait=0" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe></div>
                <div class="swiper-slide"><%= image_tag 'carousel-1.jpg' %></div>
                <!-- <div class="swiper-slide"><%= image_tag 'carousel-2.jpg' %></div> -->
                <!-- <div class="swiper-slide"><%= image_tag 'carousel-3.jpg' %></div> -->
                <div class="swiper-slide"><%= image_tag 'carousel-4.jpg' %></div>
                <div class="swiper-slide"><%= image_tag 'carousel-5.jpg' %></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="swiper-pagination"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div id="collections" class="background custom-container">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col">
        <h1>COLLECTIONS</h1>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row marginBottom100 parallax-element-detected">
      <% @collections.each do |collection| %>
        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 marginTop50 parallax-element">
          <%= link_to jewelries_pages_path(anchor: collection.name == 'African Mermaid' ? 'African' : collection.name) do %>
            <div class="collections-img-wrapper mx-auto">
              <%= image_tag collection.picture.url(:medium) %>
              <div class="collections-img-mask"></div>
              <p class="collection-name text-center"><%= collection.name %></p>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="inter-section inter-section-1">
  <div class="parallax-bg-2"></div>
</div>
<div id="about" class="background custom-container">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-12">
        <h1>ABOUT</h1>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row marginTop50 parallax-element-detected">
      <div class="col">
        <p class="parallax-element">
          As far as I can remember, I have always loved creating and working with
          my own hands. I could stayed confined in my bedroom for days to finish
          any type of artistic projects. <br> I took multiple drawing and creation
          design classes as I grew up, each one of them were enriching and
          fulfilling . They made me realize that this is what I wanted to do, this
          is what I wanted to be.
        </p>
        <p class="parallax-element">
          After four years studying in France I obtained a bachelor degree in Jewelry
          Design. At "La SEPR Lyon", where Iâ€™ve learned the history of jewelry and
          the transformation of the techniques through ages as well as studying and
          using them for my own purpose. <br> What I love the most about Jewelry
          is finding the inspiration in a lots of very different and unusual domain,
          make it my own then retransform, mix ideas and theme before the realization
          of the piece itself.<br> For about three years I have been experiencing,
          discovering, self teaching and working in various field, trying to express
          my own personality through jewelry creation.
        </p>
        <p class="parallax-element">
          Each piece of jewelry were design and hand made in New York by myself. <br>
          And I finally present to you a part of my work.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row marginTop100 marginBottom100 align-items-center parallax-element-detected">
      <div class="col-12 marginBottom50">
        <p class="parallax-element">Who helped me with the video realization?</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 text-center">
        <%= image_tag 'logo-vara.png', class: 'parallax-element logo logo-vara' %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-6 text-center">
        <%= image_tag 'logo-flora.jpg', class: 'parallax-element logo' %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 text-center">
        <%= image_tag 'logo-rebecca.jpg', class: 'parallax-element logo' %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 text-center">
        <%= image_tag 'logo-renan.png', class: 'parallax-element logo' %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="inter-section inter-section-2">
  <div class="parallax-bg-2"></div>
</div>
